{"tid":216012,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得呢句說話講得好啱?","createTime":"2017-04-24T20:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T22:05:13.000Z","uid":31739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9816f936e70fef4e8344244655e5666839668307","tid":216012,"uid":31739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T20:12:47.000Z","msg":"From Avicii - The Nights<br />\n'When I was sixteen my father said you can do whatever you want with your life. You just have to be minded you have to work hard to get it. That's when I decided when I died, I wanna be remembered for the life I lived, not the money I made.'<br />\n<br />\n深夜有感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n記得係另一個post見到有巴打講左句:<br />\n「世界係一本書，唔去旅行嘅人只係睇左其中一頁」<br />\n係到想鼓勵下各位去勇敢嘗試做自己想做嘅野 <br />\n可能係去旅行，可能係玩音樂，可能係做運動員 whatsoever<br />\n<br />\n有日同個friend講開點解香港運動風氣咁差<br />\n得出個結論係因為香港每個老母都叫個仔唔撚好做運動員，無論個仔有幾鍾意玩運動都好<br />\n但其實每個人嘅生命都係自己去define<br />\n一件事嘅價值係應該由自己去訂<br />\n各位 想做就去做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好到左五六十歲先黎後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好啦9up完<br />\n不如大家分享下自己有咩好想做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"185f7ebc79c843d6cc4bb890a98c61578691c829","tid":216012,"uid":4435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T20:15:58.000Z","msg":"想去旅行"},{"pid":"57ee95a4a6d424cdb4c91c1689cd0b0d710d2425","tid":216012,"uid":31739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T20:17:52.000Z","msg":"附上熱血playlist<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UtF6Jej8yb4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUtF6Jej8yb4&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=ff0f30db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UtF6Jej8yb4</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nsA3ue-hihE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnsA3ue-hihE&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=a0614da6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nsA3ue-hihE</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0lE_0qjXAiA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0lE_0qjXAiA&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=3ef60817\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0lE_0qjXAiA</a><br />\n<br />\n試下合埋眼，聽下呢幾首歌，再諗下自己想做嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"343b317d1b3faa5b1efb7eadbad4e64e9cb68f18","tid":216012,"uid":14716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T20:35:28.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"66c72155e4875ca679383a9e47593e0723799ff2","tid":216012,"uid":31739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T21:20:51.000Z","msg":"推 想多d人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c79e18fc4dc7fada7309eff6d9a5de4f78781dd1","tid":216012,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T21:22:32.000Z","msg":"the nights好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52798e30174a353f82cb8b91cd9e9e7b5abaa976","tid":216012,"uid":45966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T21:22:41.000Z","msg":"搵唔到伴點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc60039dbdf57a98aa5997f7d65fa0f74966cc6","tid":216012,"uid":31739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T21:33:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵唔到伴點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\